edu.uga.dawgtrades.model

Interface Membership

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable

    public interface Membership
extends Persistable
    This interface represents a Membership in DawgTrades. It has a collection of methods to read/write Membership's attributes. There must be only one Membership object (singleton). It also extends the Persistable interface, since objects of this class will be stored in the persistent data store.
